---
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Public Code US - Demand Transparency in Government Software"
	description="Join the movement for public code and transparency in US government. Sign the petition to require publicly funded software to be publicly owned."
	currentPage="/"
>
	{/* Hero Section */}
	<section class="bg-nb-cyan border-b-4 border-nb-dark">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 md:py-32">
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase italic leading-none text-nb-dark mb-6">
				Public Money.<br />
				<span class="text-nb-pink">Public Code.</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-nb-dark mb-8 max-w-2xl">
				Your tax dollars shouldn't be locked in proprietary software. Demand transparency, security, and innovation. Sign the petition for public code in America.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
				<a href="/sign" class="btn-nb btn-nb-primary inline-block text-center">
					Sign the Petition
				</a>
				<a href="/learn" class="btn-nb inline-block text-center">
					Learn Why It Matters
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* Problem Section */}
	<section class="bg-nb-light border-b-4 border-nb-dark">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-12 text-center">
				The Problem
			</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
				{/* Card 1 */}
				<div class="card-nb bg-nb-yellow">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">No Transparency</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark">
						Government software is developed behind closed doors with public money. Citizens can't see what they're paying for.
					</p>
				</div>

				{/* Card 2 */}
				<div class="card-nb bg-nb-pink text-nb-light">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4">Duplicated Work</h3>
					<p class="font-bold">
						Every state and city rebuilds the same solutions from scratch. Wasted millions while communities need resources elsewhere.
					</p>
				</div>

				{/* Card 3 */}
				<div class="card-nb bg-nb-purple text-nb-light">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4">Security Risks</h3>
					<p class="font-bold">
						Closed-source code can't be audited by security experts. Vulnerabilities hide in the dark, endangering citizen data.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* Benefits Section */}
	<section class="bg-nb-cyan border-b-4 border-nb-dark">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-12 text-center">
				Why Public Code Matters
			</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				{/* Benefit 1 */}
				<div class="border-4 border-nb-dark bg-nb-light p-6 shadow-nb">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-3">Democratic Accountability</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark">
						Public software should be subject to public scrutiny. Citizens deserve to know how their government works.
					</p>
				</div>

				{/* Benefit 2 */}
				<div class="border-4 border-nb-dark bg-nb-light p-6 shadow-nb">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-3">Economic Efficiency</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark">
						Open code can be shared across agencies and states. One solution solves multiple problems. Billions in savings.
					</p>
				</div>

				{/* Benefit 3 */}
				<div class="border-4 border-nb-dark bg-nb-light p-6 shadow-nb">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-3">Better Security</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark">
						Open-source code gets audited by thousands of eyes. Vulnerabilities are found and fixed. Proprietary is blind.
					</p>
				</div>

				{/* Benefit 4 */}
				<div class="border-4 border-nb-dark bg-nb-light p-6 shadow-nb">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-3">Innovation & Jobs</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark">
						Public code attracts developers and entrepreneurs. Creates tech jobs. Builds local tech ecosystems.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* Statistics Section */}
	<section class="bg-nb-dark text-nb-light border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic mb-12 text-center">The Scale</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
				<div>
					<p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black italic mb-2">$8.8T</p>
					<p class="font-bold text-lg">Economic value of open source software globally</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black italic mb-2">96%</p>
					<p class="font-bold text-lg">Of enterprise code bases use open source</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black italic mb-2">Billions</p>
					<p class="font-bold text-lg">Wasted on duplicate government software</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* CTA Section */}
	<section class="bg-nb-pink border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-nb-light">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase italic mb-6">
				Join the Movement
			</h2>
			<p class="text-lg font-bold mb-8">
				Demand that governments invest public money in public code. Sign the petition. Share with your network. Push for change.
			</p>
			<a href="/sign" class="btn-nb btn-nb-yellow inline-block text-center">
				Add Your Signature Now
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
